column5: Seems alot of us are going the first or second week in June. I will be up there the 7th. Anyone interested in doing a shorelunch of walleye central guys and gals? It would be cool to put faces behind some of the handles.BYOF!<{{}}><
I'll be up there the 7th through the 13th. I'd be interested.
Shucks, won't be up there till the week of July 12th, have fun guys!
BYOHFW!! Bring Your Own Hot F#$%!&* Wings!!!!! Wish I could be there.
It seems that I might be working up there this year, so yes I'd love to arrange somthing like that. You'll find I'm not near as volatile on the lake as I am in front of the computer, but hey, who is?
Good one mike! They might just need the wings!
Yeah Bill, that's kinda what I was getting at. Hope the walleye bite is a little better than last Aug. or bring lots of chicken!
Count me in. Group of 6 will be up there the 7-11. Staying at Paradise 1. Sounds like a good idea.
Sorry, not going till the 21st. Have one cool beverage for me Reels!
Will do Woods, we'll miss you.The rest of the bunch, how about Tuesday weather permitting up at Big Sand at the Beach? (N-NE Corner)<{{}}><
